org.sxb.bean

インタフェース InitializingBean

  • 既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    AbstractCacheManager, AbstractTransactionSupportingCacheManager, CompositeCacheManager, ConfigurableMimeFileTypeMap, DefaultManagedAwareThreadFactory, DefaultManagedTaskExecutor, DefaultManagedTaskScheduler, DefaultRedisScript, ExecutorConfigurationSupport, ExecutorConfigurationSupport, Jackson2ObjectMapperFactoryBean, JedisConnectionFactory, JndiObjectLocator, MessageListenerAdapter, RedisAccessor, RedisCacheManager, RedisCollectionFactoryBean, RedisMessageListenerContainer, RedisTemplate, ScheduledExecutorFactoryBean, ScheduledTaskRegistrar, SimpleCacheManager, StringRedisTemplate, ThreadPoolExecutorFactoryBean, ThreadPoolTaskExecutor, ThreadPoolTaskExecutor, ThreadPoolTaskScheduler, TransactionAwareCacheManagerProxy

    public interface InitializingBean
    Interface to be implemented by beans that need to react once all their properties have been set by a BeanFactory: for example, to perform custom initialization, or merely to check that all mandatory properties have been set.

    An alternative to implementing InitializingBean is specifying a custom init-method, for example in an XML bean definition. For a list of all bean lifecycle methods, see the BeanFactory javadocs.

    作成者:
    Jeffson

    • メソッドの詳細

      • afterPropertiesSet

        void afterPropertiesSet()
                 throws java.lang.Exception
        Invoked by a BeanFactory after it has set all bean properties supplied (and satisfied BeanFactoryAware and ApplicationContextAware).

        This method allows the bean instance to perform initialization only possible when all bean properties have been set and to throw an exception in the event of misconfiguration.

        例外:
        java.lang.Exception - in the event of misconfiguration (such as failure to set an essential property) or if initialization fails.
